text: Harald Ringstorff (born 25 September 1939) is a German politician of the SPD. He was born in Wittenburg, Mecklenburg. He was the 3rd Minister President of the state of Mecklenburg-Vorpommern. He was the 61st President of the Bundesrat in 2006/07. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians of the Social Democratic Party of Germany Category:Politicians from Mecklenburg-Vorpommern
